  
BUILDING DOCKER IMAGE

sekarang demo menggunakan python  
buat folder baru di workspace  
![][image1]

masuk ke dalam folder yang di buat  
cd  my-phython-app/

buat projek   
sudo nano app.py  
![][image2]

paste coding ini di dalam app.py  
`from flask import Flask, jsonify`

`app = Flask(__name__)`

`@app.route('/hello', methods=['GET'])`  
`def hello_world():`  
    `response = {`  
        `"return_code": 200,`  
        `"message": "hello world"`  
    `}`  
    `return jsonify(response)`

`if __name__ == '__main__':`  
    `app.run(host='0.0.0.0', port=5000)`

![][image3]

sudo nano Dockerfile  
![][image4]  
copy perintah ini  
`# Use an official Python runtime as a parent image`  
`FROM python:3.9-slim`

`# Set the working directory in the container`  
`WORKDIR /app`

`# Copy the current directory contents into the container at /app`  
`COPY . /app`

`# Install any needed packages specified in requirements.txt`  
`RUN pip install --no-cache-dir flask`

`# Make port 5000 available to the world outside this container`  
`EXPOSE 5000`

`# Define environment variable`  
`ENV NAME=World`

`# Run app.py when the container launches`  
`CMD ["python", "app.py"]`

![][image5]  
jika sudah selesai buka file nya di vscode

docker build \-t My-phython-app .  
![][image6]

berhasil di build  
![][image7]

lalu buka cek docker images  
docker images  
![][image8]  
cari file yang baru di buat tadi. kebetulan ada file sama yang ada di pling atas

oracle@oracle:\~/Workspace/my-python-app$ docker run \-dp 5000:5000 \--name python-app-container my-python-app  
![][image9]  
 docker ps  
image sudah jadi  
![][image10]  
buka browser dan tada sudah terinstall  
![][image11]

Tugas INSTALL Laravel dengan Docker

Download file tersebut   
https://gitlab.com/abdul110/bds-devops-project-tugas-9

![][image12]

 

Download file ini lalu simpan di Folder Workspace atau di mana pun ituhh.

Lalu jangan lupa unzip

Jika tidak download file tersebut lalu masukan ke file git kalian sendiri. Jangan lupa di pull

![][image13]

Lalu buat file Dockerfile

isi nya  
\# Menggunakan base image PHP 8.1  
FROM php:8.1

\# Install dependencies  
RUN apt-get update \-y && apt-get install \-y \\  
    openssl \\  
    zip \\  
    unzip \\  
    git \\  
    libonig-dev \\  
    nodejs \\  
    npm && \\  
    apt-get clean && rm \-rf /var/lib/apt/lists/\*

\# Install Composer secara global  
RUN curl \-sS https://getcomposer.org/installer | php \-- \--install-dir=/usr/local/bin \--filename=composer

\# Install PHP extensions yang dibutuhkan  
RUN docker-php-ext-install pdo mbstring

\# Set working directory  
WORKDIR /app

\# Copy seluruh project ke dalam container  
COPY . /app

\# Install dependencies composer  
RUN composer install \--no-interaction \--prefer-dist \--optimize-autoloader

\# Install dependencies npm  
RUN npm install && npm run build

\# Expose port aplikasi Laravel  
EXPOSE 8282

\# Jalankan aplikasi Laravel menggunakan artisan  
CMD \["php", "artisan", "serve", "--host=0.0.0.0", "--port=8282"\]

![][image14]

buat file .env   
tinggal copy file .env.example   
![][image15]

Build docker  
docker build \-t laravel-belajar .  
![][image16]  
jika berhasil run container nyah  
docker run \-dp 8282:8282 laravel-belajar   
[http://localhost:8282/](http://localhost:8282/)  
laravel berhasil ter devlop  
![][image17]

Menhubungkah ke database  
buat koneksi db terlebih dahulu di file .env laravel seperti ini

![][image18]

membuat network  
docker network create \-d bridge my-net  
![][image19]

cek network docker atau inspek  
docker inspect my-net  
![][image20]

daftar id network  
docker network ls

![][image21]

build ulang projeck docket laravel tadi karna baru sajah edit  file .env

![][image22]

![][image23]  
docker run \-dp 8282:8282 \--name My-Laravel \--network my-net laravel-belajar  
![][image24]

![][image25]

docker run \--name container-mysql \--network my-net \-e MYSQL\_ROOT\_PASSWORD=oracle \-d mysql

![][image26]  
buka  
 docker exec \-it My-Laravel sh  
![][image27]  
lalu jalankan perintah   
 php artisan migrate  
![][image28]  
![][image29]  
instalasi selesai di lakukan
